<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8">
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
		<title>Applicant Account Activation | AuthenticPage</title>
		<style>
			@media screen and(max-width: 600px) {
				.container {
					width: 100% !important;
				}
				.button {
					width: 100% !important;
				}
			}
			.button {
				display: inline-block;
				padding: 10px 20px;
				background-color: #4F46E5;
				color: #ffffff;
				text-decoration: none;
				border-radius: 4px;
				text-align: center;
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body style="margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #F3F4F6; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; color: #374151;">
		<table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%">
			<tr>
				<td style="padding: 20px 0;">
					<table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="600" style="margin: 0 auto; background-color: #ffffff; border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden;" class="container">
						<tr>
							<td style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4F46E5, #6366F1); padding: 32px 20px; text-align: center;">
								<img src="https://authenticpage.com/logo_528.png" alt="AuthenticPage Logo" style="width: 120px; height: auto; margin-bottom: 16px;">
								<h1 style="color: #ffffff; margin: 0;">New Applicant Account</h1>
							</td>
						</tr>
						<tr>
							<td style="padding: 20px;">
								<p style="margin: 0;">Hello
									{{ name }},</p>
								<p>Thank you for choosing AuthenticPage! We're delighted to have you as one of our users.</p>
								<p>To start using your
									<strong>Applicant</strong>
									account, please activate it by clicking the button below:</p>

								<table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%" style="margin: 32px 0;">
									<tr>
										<td align="center">
											<a href="{{ activationUrl }}" style="background-color: #4F46E5; color: #ffffff; padding: 14px 32px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 600; display: inline-block;" class="button">Activate my account</a>
										</td>
									</tr>
								</table>
								<p>Once your account is activated, you will be able to:</p>
								<ul style="padding-left: 20px; margin-bottom: 24px;">
									<li>Manage your authentication requests</li>
									<li>Access your personalized dashboard</li>
									<li>Update your information</li>
								</ul>
								<p>If you didn't request the creation of this account, please ignore this email or contact our support team.</p>
								<p>For any questions or assistance, don't hesitate to contact us at support@authenticpage.com.</p>

							</td>
						</tr>
						{% include './footer.html.twig' %}
					</table>
				</td>
			</tr>
		</table>
	</body>
</html>
